			<p><strong><span class="smallcaps">Michelle Cacho-Negrete</span></strong> lives in Wells, Maine, and her essays appear in <em>The Sun</em>&rsquo;s new book <em>The Mysterious Life of the Heart</em> and in <em>Thoreau&rsquo;s Legacy</em>, an anthology from the nonprofit Union of Concerned Scientists. She teaches writing both in person and online and is recovering well from surgery, thanks to Dr. Jeff Thurlow.</p><a href="/contributors/michelle-cacho-negrete" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
